data.description: ***Please submit all offers by 5PM Monday 12/18/23***Highly sought-after home in Rancho San Diego. This two story family home is in a prime location, featuring a light, bright, and open floor plan with vaulted ceilings in the living room, a formal dining space, and an open family room.  The home also features all 3 bedrooms upstairs, with an optional 4th bedroom. Windows everywhere! Newer A/C and paid solar.  Cute yard with low maintenance.
